quran[7{c,v,t}:
16,73,aur khuda ke siwa aison ko pujte hain jo un ko asmano aur zameen mein rozi dainay ka zara bhi ikhtiyar nahi rakhtay aur nah kisi aur terhan ka Maqdoor rakhtay hain
16,74,to ( logo ) khuda ke baray mein ( ghalat ) misalein nah banaao. ( sahih misalon ka tareeqa ) khuda hi jaanta hai aur tum nahi jantay
16,75,khuda aik aur misaal bayan farmata hai ke aik ghulam hai jo ( bilkul ) dosray ke ikhtiyar mein hai aur kisi cheez par qudrat nahi rakhta aur aik aisa shakhs hai jis ko hum ne apne haan se ( bohat sa ) maal Tayyab ataa farmaya hai aur woh is mein se ( raat din ) posheeda aur zahir kharch karta rehta hai tokiya yeh dono shakhs barabar hain? ( hargiz nahi ) Al Hamdo Lillah lekin un mein se aksar log nahi samajh rakhtay
16,76,aur khuda aik aur misaal bayan farmata hai ke do aadmi hain aik unn mein se goonga ( aur dosray ki malik ) hai ( be ikhtiyar o natawan ) ke kisi cheez par qudrat nahi rakhta. aur apne maalik ko dobhr ho raha hai woh jahan ussay bhejta hai ( kher se kabhi ) bhalai nahi lata.kiya aisa ( goonga berha ) aur woh shakhs jo ( santa boltaa aur ) logon ko insaaf karne ka hukum deta hai aur khud seedhay rastay par chal raha hai dono barabar hain ?
16,77,aur asmano aur zameen ka ilm khuda hi ko hai aur ( khuda ke nazdeek ) qayamat ka aana yun hai jaisay aankhh ka jhapakna balkay is se bhi jald tar. kuch shak nahi ke khuda har cheez par Qadir hai
16,78,aur khuda hi ne tum ko tumhari maaon ke shikam se pedakiya ke tum kuch nahi jantay they. aur is ne tum ko kaan aur ankhen aur dil ( aur unn ke ilawa aur ) aaza bakhshay taakay tum shukar karo
16,79,kiya un logon ne parindon ko nahi dekha ke aasman ki howa mein ghiry hue ( urtye rehtay ) hain. un ko khuda hi thaamay rakhta hai. imaan walon ke liye is mein ( bohat si ) nishanain hain
